text: Nasim Pedrad (; born November 18, 1981) is an Iranian-born American actress and comedian. She was born in Tehran, Iran and emigrated to Irvine, California in 1984. She is best known for her five seasons as a cast member on Saturday Night Live from 2009 to 2014. After SNL, she went on to co-star in sitcoms such as Mulaney, Scream Queens, People of Earth, and New Girl. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Naturalized citizens of the United States Category:Actors from Tehran Category:Actors from Orange County, California Category:Comedians from California Category:People from Irvine, California
